  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205150/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.poster.avif?t=1711562903\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205150/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.webm?t=1711562903\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205150/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.mp4?t=1711562903\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What kind of game is PlanetBlight</h2>?PlanetBlight is a first-person survival game<br><br>To explore and survive, players must gather the remaining resources on the infected planet, investigate buildings and facilities, and craft the equipment they need to survive.<br>Players must be prepared for danger at all times, and against the threat of marauders, players must build strongholds or craft powerful weapons and armor,<br>Gun attachments and customizations that can be unlocked using skill points earned as players level up, allowing them to shoot more accurately and reliably in combat.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205150/extras/8c257ecf13f538c7041258ca069864df.poster.avif?t=1711562903\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205150/extras/8c257ecf13f538c7041258ca069864df.webm?t=1711562903\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205150/extras/8c257ecf13f538c7041258ca069864df.mp4?t=1711562903\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://share